																	</hgroup>
							</header>
							<p>
								The governors plan to launch a team by this summer to jointly compile measures to fight the pandemic.								<a href="https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2020/06/04/national/japan-governors-balancing-revival-virus/" class="more_link"><span class="icon-arrow-2"></span></a>
